Title: Mow the lawn
Description: Use the lawnmower to cut the grass in the front and back yard.

Title: Vacuum the living room
Description: Vacuum the carpet and clean any visible debris.

Title: Do the laundry
Description: Wash, dry, and fold the clothes.

Title: Water the plants
Description: Check the soil moisture and water the indoor and outdoor plants as needed.

Title: Organize the pantry
Description: Arrange food items neatly and check for expired products.

Title: Clean the bathroom
Description: Scrub the toilet, sink, shower, and bathtub.

Title: Dust the furniture
Description: Wipe down surfaces and remove dust from furniture.

Title: Walk the dog
Description: Take the dog for a walk around the neighborhood.
